List.Description:
Silky smooth California Merlot makes the perfect match for parmesan peppercorn cheese, delicious water crackers and Ghirardelli chocolate in this classic gift.

California Dreaming Wine Trio
List.Description:
We've gathered three top wines from select regions in California, representing grape varieties California does best. Wines include: Clos la Chance Monterey Chardonnay, LangeTwins Zinfandel and L de Lyeth Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon.

Wine Set Includes:
  • Monterey Chardonnay: Clos la Chance
    A burst of tropical fruit on the nose. Pineapple and banana with a hint of mango and coconut. Very refreshing on the palate. The wine is aged only in stainless steel (no oak) so the fruit really shines through, along with the bright acidity.
  • Lodi Zinfandel: Lange Twins
    LangeTwins Zinfandel shows an array of berry aromas and flavors including red raspberry, black cherry and spice. It finishes with lasting vanilla notes.
  • Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon: L de Lyeth
    The diverse Sonoma County delivers a range of wines, but top among those is Cabernet Sauvignon. This well-balanced Cabernet offers luscious fruit, with layers of wild berry, black currant and a hint of toast. With a nice tannin structure and a harmonious finish, this wine is ready to enjoy!
  • Printed Insert that describes the featured wines

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Dom Perignon and Godiva are legendary brands that have set the standard for combining luxury with heavenly taste. Beautifully packaged, the Godiva 8-piece Gold Ballotin includes a variety of milk, dark, and white chocolates with classic Belgian fillings such as silky ganaches, creamy pralines, rich caramels, fruits, and nuts.
